        <heading>Miscellaneous Tax Provisions</heading>
        <section eId="sec_12_497a">
          <num>12-497a</num>
          <heading>Exemptions</heading>
          <subsection eId="12_497a__subsec_a">
            <num>(a)</num>
            <content>
              <p>The tax imposed by section12-494and the requirement of filing a return pursuant to section12-497shall not apply to the transfer of burial rights for a lot in a cemetery organized pursuant to chapter 368j.</p>
            </content>
          </subsection>
          <subsection eId="12_497a__subsec_b">
            <num>(b)</num>
            <content>
              <p>The requirement of filing a return pursuant to section12-497shall not apply to any deed, instrument or writing which is solely a grant of easement and to which this state or any of its political subdivisions or its or their respective agencies is a party.
